{"tid":844427,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國續羞辱天主教徒　河南教堂辦佛教儀式","createTime":"2018-10-02T01:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T03:45:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5a00d9a80762581a4646726f2ed30e77589047d4","tid":844427,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T01:01:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181002/640_1bd19837c0b2c9c7430f77663a959766.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181002%2F640_1bd19837c0b2c9c7430f77663a959766.jpg&h=c1e1e97d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梵蒂岡早前才與中國簽訂任命主教臨時協議，沒想到馬上傳出中國地方政府打壓當地的天主教徒。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台（RFA）近日於官方推特上，貼出一段在河南拍攝的影片，顯示當地一家天主教堂，不但內、外被拆除十字架，當局周日（30日）更安排佛教徒在教堂內進行佛教儀式。從影片可見，有僧侶在教堂內誦經，現場也有其他和尚和信徒。<br />\n<br />\n有網友直言，這是中國打壓天主教和基督教的最新方式，不但有褻瀆意圖，還能製造各宗教之間的矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181002/1439891/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181002%2F1439891%2F&d=P1GZ2xwQnzPT8eOpEw7DJ2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=487eeaa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181002%2F1439891%2F&h=4c0436ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181002/1439891/</a>"},{"pid":"77812a8938a5bed2bed5c8795131e4cef16bcec5","tid":844427,"uid":33483,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T01:05:27.000Z","msg":"班撚樣真係專搞屎棍"},{"pid":"36c5de5270aa96521cf1cfd224faf4add6bba853","tid":844427,"uid":108305,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T01:15:25.000Z","msg":"同索菲亞大教堂變清真寺差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9d9f0e907a3dcfff0d6b69edf2ab757840bc93","tid":844427,"uid":62532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2